{"tid":2037211,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔贊成今日出港島","createTime":"2020-05-27T00:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:51:58.000Z","uid":30122,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12a79674ea1894d0dd95ae03a74bf679e0804a16","tid":2037211,"uid":30122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:57:37.000Z","msg":"抱歉我能力不足，而家先諗到點講。<br />\n<br />\n今日發生咩事就大家都知，但如果而家出港島，衰啲講句，就係&rdquo;喺對家指定嘅時間，喺對方指定嘅地方出現&rdquo;，以今日共匪嘅部署來講，出金鐘肯定無咩好結果，而打仗都肯定唔係咁打<br />\n<br />\n今日手足嘅目的係阻止立法會開會，我認為係失敗嘅，而失敗嘅原因，其實係手足太遲去諗點樣應付今日，所以只係得番而家出金鐘嘅選項。而當手足只有呢個選項，對家部署就係簡單同輕鬆。<br />\n<br />\n而家要另外諗計都難，今日只適合喺其他區做和平抗爭而已。<br />\n<br />\n至於勇武，我認為要將眼光放喺下星期，而家就諗定於下星期要做咩，例如想阻止立法會開會，真係只能喺開會時間出金鐘？能否令立法會一段時間用唔到呢？而家就可以諗點做，時間自己決定。<br />\n<br />\n咁就係將抗爭主導權交給自己，咁手足先會更安全。"},{"pid":"1aa2ff3c31243c06dc477c0675ad4151996b69e9","tid":2037211,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:58:22.000Z","msg":"等睇你俾人屌係分化撚！五毛！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4eb4f9d4afda9edc772c555d2072a81733adbde","tid":2037211,"uid":203685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:59:58.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得勇武手足可以轉場去旺角<br />\n因為依家金鐘真係太多狗"},{"pid":"4a64f10813d2b44665ede25a86d8fc4131ec3efe","tid":2037211,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peT8V93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeT8V93.png&h=419e79fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6b9d47465d3e7737270c004bb603c43d89d4e3e","tid":2037211,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:01:31.000Z","msg":"［互相配合］五毛：送頭，狗：人少左，方便拉人，逐個擊破<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a236778b975f8d0bddd7b9ede182bf9014e895cc","tid":2037211,"uid":9435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:04:16.000Z","msg":"你唔好出年先講<br />\nBlock"},{"pid":"91ebeac8c01f30d9afe6e147ecc837f13cd27b40","tid":2037211,"uid":30122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"我想手足今日就開始為下星期，下下星期部署，反正而家立法會唔慌有好事發生"}]}